The '''Jungle Clans''' were a group of [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] clans that joined together to ally with the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] and its successor, the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]], against the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[Yuuzhan Vong War|invaders]].

